        "subject": "LU-5420 mgc: MGC should retry for invalid import",
        "message": "LU-5420 mgc: MGC should retry for invalid import\n\nSince MGC import is not fully replayable, (i.e. the import might\nbe evicted during recovery) mgc_process_log() should retry calls\nto mgc_enqueue() (for retrieving config log) until the import is\nfully recovered or closed.\n\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/11258\n\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I8dbcafbda362ebbd3370e7527a3c14c594500c1e\n"
      },
